```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df_orders = pd.DataFrame({
    "store": (["A"]*14) + (["B"]*14),
    "date": pd.to_datetime(
        ["2025-11-01","2025-11-02","2025-11-03","2025-11-04","2025-11-05","2025-11-06","2025-11-07",
         "2025-11-08","2025-11-09","2025-11-10","2025-11-11","2025-11-12","2025-11-13","2025-11-14"]*2
    ),
    "orders": (
        # Store A: Ï†ïÏ±Ö ÌõÑ Ï£ºÎ¨∏ Ï¶ùÍ∞Ä
        [100,102,98,101,99,100,101, 110,112,115,118,120,122,125] +
        # Store B: Í±∞Ïùò Î≥ÄÌôî ÏóÜÏùå
        [90,91,89,90,92,90,91, 92,91,90,93,92,91,90]
    ),
    "revenue": (
        # A
        [1000,1010,980,1005,995,1000,1005, 1150,1170,1200,1230,1250,1280,1300] +
        # B
        [900,905,890,900,920,900,910, 915,910,905,925,920,910,905]
    )
})
df_policy = pd.DataFrame({
    "store": ["A","B"],
    "policy_date": pd.to_datetime(["2025-11-08", "2025-11-08"]),
    "is_treated": [True, False]   # AÎßå Ï†ïÏ±Ö Ï†ÅÏö©, BÎäî ÎåÄÏ°∞Íµ∞
})

display(df_orders, df_policy)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
df_merged = df_orders.merge(df_policy, how='left', on ='store')
display(df_merged.head())
df_merged['is_post'] = df_merged['date']>=df_merged['policy_date']
display(df_merged.head())
df_merged['aov'] = df_merged['revenue']/df_merged['orders']
display(df_merged.head())
store_feat = df_merged.groupby(['store', 'is_treated', 'is_post']).agg(
    orders_mean=('orders','mean'),
    revenue_mean=('revenue','mean'),
    aov_mean = ('aov','mean')
).reset_index()
display(store_feat)
treated = store_feat[store_feat['is_treated']]
treated_pivot = treated.pivot(
    index='store',
    columns='is_post',
    values=['orders_mean','revenue_mean','aov_mean']
)

display(treated_pivot)
policy_effect = pd.DataFrame({
    'store': treated_pivot.index,
    'delta_orders'  : treated_pivot[('orders_mean', True)]
                     - treated_pivot[('orders_mean', False)],
    'delta_revenue' : treated_pivot[('revenue_mean', True)]
                     - treated_pivot[('revenue_mean', False)],
    'delta_aov'     : treated_pivot[('aov_mean', True)]
                     - treated_pivot[('aov_mean', False)],
}).reset_index(drop=True)

display(policy_effect)
policy_effect['effect_flag'] = (policy_effect['delta_orders'] > 5 ) & (policy_effect['delta_revenue']>100)
display(policy_effect)
```
